      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- data from coming from an API\n    fetch xhr - \n- geolocation\n\n\"Monkey Patches\" common browser APIs.\n    \n- replace the browser's fetch with a new function called fetch\n\n\nfetch(...args) {\n    fetch(...args);\n       triggerChangeDetection()\n}\n\ndoSomething() {\n    new Promise(...);\n}\n\nawait doSomething();\n// do this other other then.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- data from coming from an API\n    fetch xhr - \n- geolocation\n\n\"Monkey Patches\" common browser APIs.\n    \n- replace the browser's fetch with a new function called fetch\n\n\nfetch(...args) {\n    fetch(...args);\n       triggerChangeDetection()\n}\n\ndoSomething() {\n    new Promise(...);\n}\n\nawait doSomething();\n// do this other other then.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "k6Nmk_FE_YnClckXP7owk",
